akas: Transformers: Rescue Bots - Mission Protection! France
akas from release info: Transformers: Rescue Bots - Mission Protection! France

1.title: New Normal
1.plot: Three years after their arrival on Earth, an alien attack forces the Rescue Bots to decide whether to reveal their true natures to the citizens of Griffin Rock.

2.title: Bridge Building
2.plot: While the citizens of Griffin Rock decide whether or not to let the Bots stay in their midst, a GroundBridge accident splits the Team.

3.title: Arrivals
3.plot: As Frankie struggles to adjust to life with her baby sister, the Bots are surprised by a new arrival of their own.

4.title: Plus One
4.plot: Quickshadow upsets the Rescue Team's dynamic when Heatwave invites her to take a turn at leadership.

5.title: Back to Virtual Reality
5.plot: When Dani's out-of-this-world test flight doesn't go according to plan, the Rescue Team is her only hope of ever making it back home.

6.title: Vanishing Returns
6.plot: The Bots deal with a group of investors who want to build a vacation resort in Griffin Rock, while Cody deals with feeling invisible around everyone.

7.title: Ghost in the Machine
7.plot: As Griffin Rock celebrates their version of Halloween, Evan and Myles car-jack Quickshadow and discover the Bots' secret.

8.title: Enemy of My Enemy
8.plot: The Burns family finds an unexpected ally in a former foe when the Rescue Bots are captured by a new villain.

9.title: Mayor May Not
9.plot: The Rescue Team is distressed, and the town of Griffin Rock gets more than it bargained for, when Chase is elected as the new mayor.

10.title: All Spark Day
10.plot: While celebrating a Cybertronian holiday, the Rescue Bots take on their biggest challenge yet - a super-sized, overtired baby.

11.title: Part-Time Heroes
11.plot: When Griffin Rock's communication tower needs replacing, the Bots and Burnses take on part-time jobs to raise the money.

12.title: The More Things Change...
12.plot: The Rescue Team struggles with last minute preparations as they finally open the mainland Training Center.

13.title: The More Things Stay the Same
13.plot: The Bots' Mainland Training Center is in danger of being discovered by humans and, to make matters worse, the Rescue Team is trapped inside with a glitching hologram.

14.title: Hot Rod Bot
14.plot: Dani helps Blurr find balance between his wish to be a winning racecar and a working Rescue Bot.

15.title: King Burns
15.plot: While Chief helps Woodrow rescue gorillas from a volcanic eruption, his sons learn they are heirs to the "throne" of Griffin Rock!

16.title: Pizza Pi Party
16.plot: When Doc's new super-yeast causes havoc at Griffin Rock's Pizza Pi Festival, the Bots have to find unconventional ways to deal with a rising problem.

17.title: Uninvited Guest
17.plot: Bumblebee's unexpected appearance at the Bots' Training Center brings more than a few surprises to the Team.

18.title: Camp Cody
18.plot: When Blades is unable to participate in a Lad Pioneer leveling up ceremony on the mainland due to his Bot form, Graham and Cody help disguise him - and uncover a few more surprises along the way.

19.title: Once Upon a Time
19.plot: The Rescue Team is drawn into the woods to solve the mystery of what's making the Griffin Spruces fall... but is the answer based in science, or fairy tales?

20.title: The Need for Speed
20.plot: A mysterious criminal and unexpected visitor challenge Blurr's future as a Rescue Bot.

21.title: Cody's 11
21.plot: The Burns family and their Bots plan a heist to steal back Energon and technology that have fallen into dangerous hands.

22.title: A Brush with Danger
22.plot: Cody rides along with each of the Bots to decide what kind of rescue worker he wants to be -- but when a member of his family is in danger, Cody's true calling becomes clear.

23.title: To Infinity... And Back
23.plot: When Dani's out-of-this-world test flight doesn't go according to plan, the Rescue Team is her only hope of ever making it back home.

24.title: Family Business
24.plot: When Optimus Prime splits the Rescue Bots into different teams for new assignments, the evil genius of Doctor Morocco return to wreak havoc.

25.title: Upgrades
25.plot: The computer-generated Doctor morocco hatches a bold new plot to win against the Rescue Bots... by becoming one of them.

26.title: Transformations
26.plot: The computer-generated Doctor morocco hatches a bold new plot to win against the Rescue Bots... by becoming one of them.

1.title: Family of Heroes
1.plot: Transformers Rescue Bots follows the adventures of four young Transformers and their human counterparts- a family of emergency responders. HEATWAVE, CHASE, BLADES and BOULDER are tasked by Optimus Prime to study the ways of humanity and protect manking on the island of Griffin Rock, a highly advanced hub of technology where anything can happen. Whether it be rampaging Dinobots, volcanoes accidentally brought to life, or floating lobsters, the Rescue Bots will never hesitate to ROLL TO THE RESCUE!

25.title: It's a Bot Time
25.plot: When Doc Greene experiments with a long-hidden Time Machine, the Bots, Cody, and Frankie make an unexpected trip to 1939 Griffin Rock, where they're captured by an old nemesis who is even older than they thought! Can they escape from the past without altering the present?

26.title: Bot to the Future
26.plot: After time-traveling to 1939, Cody, Frankie, and the Rescue Bots return home to find that Griffin Rock has morphed into Moropolis--and Doctor Morocco wants to keep things that way.

19.title: Changes
19.plot: Doctor Morocco learns a devastating secret that threatens the Rescue Bots' mission, but Optimus Prime guides Heatwave to acquire a surprising new ability.

20.title: Movers and Shakers
20.plot: When rogue technology goes underground, the Rescue Team has to outwit and take down the terror lurking just beneath Griffin Rock's soil.

21.title: Odd Bot Out
21.plot: Blades feels left out when Bumblebee, on a mission to Griffin Rock, partners up with Dani.

22.title: The Griffin Rock Express
22.plot: While the Rescue Team is kept busy renovating a train tunnel from the Mainland, a mysterious Superhero watches over Griffin Rock.

23.title: Double Villainy
23.plot: Griffin Rock's most dastardly villains team up in a plan to kidnap the Rescue Bots and destroy the island.

24.title: Rise of the Heroes
24.plot: Wiped of their memories, the Rescue Bots are faced with saving Griffin Rock while believing the Burnses are their enemies.

1.title: Land Before Prime
1.plot: Optimus is forced to embrace his primal side when the Rescue Bots discover an island of dinosaurs.

2.title: Big Game
2.plot: A notorious Big Game Hunter has set his sights on Optimus Prime's new Dinosaur Mode.

3.title: Too Many Kades
3.plot: After Doc's imaging chamber produces several copies of Kade, each an extreme form of his personality, Cody and the Rescue Bots teach him a valuable lesson in teamwork.

4.title: Phantom of the Sea
4.plot: The Rescue Bots and the Burns family board a ghost ship that appears only once every ten years.

5.title: Unfinished Business
5.plot: Chase is determined to complete a space mission the Rescue Bots were forced to abandon before coming to Earth.

6.title: No Place Like Dome
6.plot: When Doc creates a giant dome to shield Griffin Rock from a hurricane, he inadvertently gives the Vigilant Computer a second chance to "protect" the island.

7.title: Bugs in the System
7.plot: Dr Moroco is causing trouble again, this time with an army that will cause problems for the team.

8.title: The Switcheroo Effect
8.plot: An encounter with a space nebula causes the Rescue Bots to switch personalities with the Burns family members.

9.title: The Riders of Midwinter
9.plot: The Bots take on new job responsibilities when the worst winter storm in centuries threatens an important Griffin Rock holiday.

10.title: Bot-Tastic Voyage
10.plot: When Kade accidently ingests microscopic cleaning robots, the Rescue Bots must go on an inner space voyage to save him.

11.title: Quarry vs. Quarry
11.plot: To rebuild his game-hunting business, Colonel Quarry tries to force Doc to build him more robotic dinosaurs. The result: Heatwave, Chase, and Blades must take on DinoBot forms.

12.title: Chief Woodrow
12.plot: Meet the Transformers Rescue Bots! Chase, Heatwave, Blades, and Boulder are given an important mission by Optimus Prime: Protect and learn about mankind. Stationed on a technologically advanced island, they team up with a family of first responders to protect their new home and along the way, they learn what it really means to be a hero.

13.title: Did You See What I Thaw?
13.plot: The Bots discover a caveman preserved in ice, but their attempts to help him adjust to modern life cause chaos in Griffin Rock.

14.title: The Attack of Humungado
14.plot: When monsters from Kade's favorite movie materialize in Griffin Rock, it's up to the DinoBots to corral the Kaiju.

15.title: Thieves Like Us
15.plot: While the Burnses are stranded at sea by a swarm of stinging jellyfish, the Bots must contend with thieving miniature souvenir replicas of themselves.

16.title: Time After Time
16.plot: A renovated Clock Tower creates hiccups in time, causing Cody to relive the same morning over and over.

17.title: Pirates Ahoy
17.plot: Meet the Transformers Rescue Bots! Chase, Heatwave, Blades, and Boulder are given an important mission by Optimus Prime: Protect and learn about mankind. Stationed on a technologically advanced island, they team up with a family of first responders to protect their new home and along the way, they learn what it really means to be a hero.

18.title: Turning the Tide
18.plot: An old friend of Optimus arrives to train the Bots in ocean rescues.

19.title: The Last of Morocco
19.plot: Cody and the Rescue Bots learn about the value of friendship when Dr. Morocco's best friend, the famous writer Jules Verne, travels through time to find him.

20.title: The New Recruits
20.plot: When a Cybertronian ship with two Autobots in stasis is discovered in a cave, the Rescue Bots find they have two new recruits to train. The newbies, however, have a dark secret.

21.title: Rescue Bots Academy
21.plot: It's up to Cody and the Rescue Bots to teach Blurr and Salvage everything they need to know before the new recruits put someone in danger.

22.title: A New Hero
22.plot: A solar flare knocks out the power to Griffin Rock; Blurr deserts the Rescue Bots and steals their ship.

23.title: Four-Legged Hero
23.plot: The undercover status of the Rescue Bots is put in danger by Servo when Mrs. Luskey's dog Poopsie starts to get involved with Servo which causes some mayhem in Griffin Rock.

24.title: Endangered Species
24.plot: Boulder's discovery of endangered woodpeckers on Griffin Rock causes the Bots to go to extremes to protect them--especially when the Mayor sees a chance for more tourist dollars.

25.title: More Than Meets the Eye
25.plot: Meet the Transformers Rescue Bots! Chase, Heatwave, Blades, and Boulder are given an important mission by Optimus Prime: Protect and learn about mankind. Stationed on a technologically advanced island, they team up with a family of first responders to protect their new home and along the way, they learn what it really means to be a hero.

26.title: I Have Heard the Robots Singing
26.plot: Doc's new invention causes everyone in town to sing instead of talk, creating confusion and tension on the Team.

27.title: Now and Then
27.plot: The Island of Griffin Rock vanishes from the ocean.

28.title: Today and Forever
28.plot: The Rescue Bots make the ultimate sacrifice to save Griffin Rock.

imdb.title: Transformers: Rescue Bots
plot: The Rescue Bots are Transformers that work with a family of heroes to rescue humans from disasters. These non-violent Transformer stories are aimed at preschool viewers.::Anonymous
